seo: 方正全媒体采编系统,信息泄露漏洞,安全检测,漏洞扫描
seo_en: Founder All-Media Editing System, information leakage vulnerability, security testing, vulnerability scanning
summary: 该插件用于检测方正全媒体采编系统是否存在信息泄露漏洞，通过检查特定接口的响应内容来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Founder All-Media Editing System has an information leakage vulnerability by checking the response content of a specific interface to confirm the existence of the vulnerability.
